S:** For a truly polished, unique design.\n*   **Write much more JavaScript:**\n    *   Implement more robust filtering and sorting logic.\n    *   Connect to a backend API to fetch tool data instead of the hardcoded array.\n    *   Implement user accounts, submissions, reviews, etc.\n    *   Integrate actual AI tools for search or recommendations (this involves backend work and API calls to services like OpenAI).\n*   **Backend Development:** A server-side application to manage the database of tools, user accounts, handle submissions, and potentially serve the AI-powered features.\n\nGood luck with your project! This should give you a tangible base to build from.",
